messages.content:
mirror for YLimits and also make a get_y_limits() function to go along with it
Here is code I selected (with carefully preserved indentation) from auto_edit/new_silence/player/segment_plotter.py:

@dataclass(frozen=True)
class XLimits:
    start: float
    end: float

    @property
    def width(self) -> float:
        return self.end - self.start

    @property
    def middle(self) -> float:
        return (self.start + self.end) / 2

    @property
    def half(self) -> float:
        return self.width / 2
